cff-version: 1.2.0
title: "IoRT-DT: Federated Digital Twins for Autonomous Underwater Vehicle Fleets"
message: >-
  If you use this software, please cite it using the metadata below.
  This software accompanies the PhD dissertation at University of Nebraska at Omaha.
